                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Slight chance of a shower. Winds westerly 15 to 20 km/h tending southwesterly 20 to 30 km/h in the morning then becoming west to southwesterly and light in the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to around 9 with daytime temperatures reaching around 18.</text>
